Award-winning Nigerian RnB singer and songwriter, Praiz born Praise Ugbede Adejo has shared insights on what keeps a man happy. Praiz who was proclaimed as the first African Artiste at the state of Minnesota revealed from his honest viewpoint that what keeps a man happy is when he is financially stable. The 37-year-old hinted that when a man has a heavy pocket, the possibility of him living a joyous and happy life is high and hemade this revelation on his official and verified Twitter page on April 15, 2021. He tweeted;
“To be honest, it’s until a man is financially stable that he’s truly happy.”